des:
Listen to this interactive story with a timeless lesson. At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. 
A little boy you name, forgets home and school as he gapes at birds in disbelief, disbelief in a reality that is a far cry, from Darwinian theories of evolution of might based fitness, as he lives in the world of birds, the little boy divorces the deceit and the mortgages of people and lives in real living land, in freedom.
